message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit you based on its value of $12000 to you. I am confident it will meet your needs and expectations. To make this opportunity available to you, I am proposing a price of $10000 for the product. This offer is exclusive to you and represents an excellent value considering its high worth to you. I look forward to your consideration and hope we can reach a mutually beneficial agreement.
